(1)给出设计进阶要求的入段显示译码器的HDL设计文体。
LIBRARY.
USE IEEE.STD-LOGZC_1164.ALL;
ENTI7Y seg7、4. IS
PORT.(DATA_in: IN STD、LOGZC_VECTOR(3 DOWNTO O);
SG_out:OUT STD-LOGZCVECTOR(7 DOWN70 0);
END;
ARCHITECTURE one. OF seg7、4 IS. BEGIN.
PROCESS(DATA-in) BEGIN.
CASE. DATA_in IS,
WHEN “0000”⇒SG-out<=“00000001”;
WHEN “0001”⇒SG-out<=“00010010”;
WHEN “0100”⇒SG-out<=“01001100”;
WHEN “0101”⇒SG-out<=“00100100”;
WHEN “0110”⇒SG.out<="00100000';
WHEN “O111”⇒SG-out<=“00001111”;
WHEN “1000”⇒SG-out<="00000000;
WHEN “1001”⇒SG.out<="00000100"
WHEN “1010”⇒SG-out<=“00000010”;
WHEN “1011”⇒SG-out<="01100000;
WHEN “1100”⇒SG-out<="01110010";
WHEN “1101”⇒SG-out<="01000000";
WHEN “1110”⇒SG-out<="00010000";
WHEN “1111”⇒SG-out<="00111000;
WHEN OTHERS⇒NULL;
END CASE ;
END PROCESS;
END;
(2),给出设计进阶要求的BCD码显示译码器的HDL设计文本.
即将括号内的删掉即可，剩下的照搬。
(3).编译出错原因:录入字符错误.,可以查看Processiny窗口的红色错误信息所有双击后.将跳至VHDL的错误所在行.,改正后.保存并再次启动编译，直到成功。
